cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NA, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with image optimization problems and their efficient solutions in the Fourier domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves mathematical background and optimization techniques, which suggests it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The paper also provides practical implementations, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
